Legend:
  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  ? = Questionable

Plans for 0.8.0
===============

  * Finder
      - ^$
      - . -> ...

  New:
    [W] Text capitalization assistant

  Changes:
    [D] Simplified and changed several keycombos
    [D] Subtitle number search now starts only on numeric key-presses
    [D] Splitting subtitle no longer duplicates texts
    [D] Fixed issue of disappearing tags when converting case
    [D] Find and replace notifications moved to main window's statusbar
    [D] Find and replace now notifies of wrapping
    [D] Toolbar style is now configurable in ~/.gaupol/gaupol.gtk.conf

  Updated translations:
    [D] Polish (pl)


Plans after 0.8.0
=================

  * Text correction assistants
     - Common error correction
     - Line reformatting
     - Hearing impaired subtitle removal


